services:
AGM Renovations offers Complete basement and Bathroom renovations packages from the professional design through the professional cleaning including:

Drywall- We employ only professional drywall installers and our goal is deliver complete satisfaction to each and every client with the quality of our workmanship and our prompt, reliable service.
    
Taping- Our drywall taping techniques will bring a high quality smooth finish, with a level of excellence you will take pride in.

Painting- We include all wall priming, painting of ceilings, baseboards, casing, crown and cove moldings into our basement construction packages
    
High Grade Laminate Flooring- is standard in our basement renovations packages.

Tiling- Shower, bathroom, or kitchenette tiling will be done by professional tile installers who are employed directly by AGM. A 2 year unlimited warranty is provided to you standard when you finish your basement with AGM
   
Plumbing- Our licensed plumbers will ensure that no problem is left unsolved and you can be sure that any drain or other plumbing defects left by the original house builder will be fixed effectively.

Electrical- We are committed to providing fully licensed electrician service as part of our standard package. Should you ever require an electrical certificate when you decide to sell your property, we will be happy to provide it to you

OGC - Ottawa General Contractors are leaders as Ottawa's design and build renovation experts. Specializing in home renovations, new and custom home construction as well as home design. With our project management and coordination, we're able to efficiently juggle more jobs, large and small, without dropping the ball. 

Ottawa General Contractors are an accredited business with the Ottawa BBB and our CEO, Moe Abbas is a former member of the board of directors for the Better Business Bureau (BBB).. Our skills and expert service has allowed us to expand to other cities in Canada including Vancouver and Calgary in less than 8 years making us one of the fastest growing construction companies. 

We offer warranty following the Tarion warranty guidelines for all our renovations and construction projects. We also have a design center and in house designers available to help you design and build your home. With over 50 years of experience, our team has the knowledge, the tools, the skill-set and the resources to give you the best value for your dollar at unbeatable service. 

We at Ottawa General Contractors understand that you are looking for value with your renovation services. Trust our team to do it right the first time! Call us directly at (613) 225-9991!

profile:
Fernand Boileau is a third generation cabinet maker and has been in this trade for over 30 years. Before going into permanent retirement, he decided to establish Boiserie SEBO Woodwork Inc. in February 2004, with the help of his two sons, Sebastien and Mathieu. He is quite proud of his achievements and first and foremost this family business.

We design, build and install custom cabinetry for kitchens and bathrooms, as well as entertainment centers and other furniture. Whether you’re planning a simple project or looking for a turn key renovation, we’ve got you covered.

Boiserie Sebo Woodwork Inc is located in Orleans. Our beautiful showroom contains an array of kitchens, vanities, bar, wine cellar and a wide array of doors and materials. The plant has been equipped with the most modern equipment to insure precision and the highest quality end product. We choose only the highest grade of materials to ensure the quality and longevity of our product.

Our experienced designers work one on one with you to create the ideal customized space to fit your budget and style. We offer free consultations, which includes them going to your home for measurements, a floor plan layout complete with 3d views of your completed project, and a price breakdown.

profile:
Your Vision, Our Expertise. Together We Can Make Your Dream Come True
At MY Kitchens, we are a team that believes in passionately providing expertise to produce a renovation that fits your home, budget and most importantly, you. We initiate with viewing our clients as partners, after discussing and analyzing our clients’ idea and expectations, we explore those ideas and then present a range of options to fulfill client inspired design solutions. We recognize that each family has different needs for their unique life styles also how important your home is, as an investment and as a personal safe haven. Your home is a reflection of who you are, the quality and details are important. We are committed to providing you a renovation experience that offers you comfort from start to finish.
services:
Our team helps you navigate the sometimes overwhelming renovation and design process using our collective expertise and experience. Our goal is to make the renovation process as easy as possible by resourcing and managing the entire project from conception, through construction, to final completion. During the process, you will work closely with your designer; project coordinator and installer to ensure your project’s success. Here’s all the service MY Kitchens provide from start to finish:
•	Design Consultation 
Book an appointment with an in store designer professional whose wealth of knowledge and experience is available to you, whether you’re looking for inspiration ideas or complete home renovations, Our design team can provide you with creative and unique options for your kitchen and bath projects.

•	Complete Design Services
After getting to know you and how you use your space. This ensures our recommendations are truly what’s best for you and your home. We will come to your house and take initial measurements and offer you 3D rendering designs of your project free of charge along with an estimate with all the work scope required in detail.

•	Product Selection
Our design team will guide you with selecting all the materials and finishes. We offer custom and semi-custom cabinetry. We also have a wide variety of options to choose from for countertops; cabinetry accessories; back splash and many more. Our goal is to create a beautiful and high functioning space for you to enjoy.

•	Project Management
We take care of all the project coordination so that you don’t have to. Any construction project has many facets that all need to come together in a cohesive way to ensure successful project completion. By having a strong project management team we ensure your project stays well on track and that the most important person, you, are kept will informed.

•	Construction
We have in-house experts for many things and we’ve built relationships with professionals in other trades to create a team that can accomplish the most difficult projects. We have working relationships with electricians, plumbers, structural engineers to help with moving load bearing walls, specialist to properly remove asbestos and more. We have the expertise to take care of projects no matter the scope.

•	After Sales Service
We take pride in meeting the expectations we’ve set. If the outcome didn’t exceed expectations, we take full responsibility until it is done right along with a 5 year warranty on any of our products. We make all decisions with the perspective that we desire long term relationships.

profile:
The owners and staff are a group of professional, dedicated and talented individuals with extensive experience in the kitchen and bathroom cabinet industry. We currently service many local custom builders and contractors, as well as some of Ottawa’s larger Builder/Developers.
We specialize in kitchen and bathroom design while offering quality products at competitive prices. We provide services that include: design consultation and conceptual drawings; on-site measuring; shop drawings; production drawings; order implementation; scheduling; delivery; installation and follow-up service. Offering a wide range of products, we are able to cater to new home builders, renovators, contractors, as well as individual homeowners.
With two cabinet manufacturers and many cabinet lines to choose from as well as a wide selection of counter tops including, laminates, Corian, Quartz and Granite, we are able to cater to your individual needs.
Cartier Kitchens cabinetry is manufactured in Brampton, Ontario and is 100% Canadian owned and operated. As an established cabinet manufacturer, Cartier has built a solid reputation in the industry. Cartier is “Quality and reliability you can trust”.
Customization without the price, Cortina Kitchens cabinetry has spent 25 years perfecting its cabinet and millwork process in order to offer you the best of both worlds. Premium hardware, old world techniques, and, hand crafted artisan finishes are but a few of the things that set them apart.
Since opening our first showroom in 2009, we have been gradually building our client base and taking on new business. Our new 2000 sq. ft. showroom in Kanata is now open to offer your clients a multitude of styles and finishes to choose from.
